To run a full schedule, simulate, correlate cycle:

1. (optional) Generate .vex file

  sched < cband1.key

2. (optional, at NRAO only) Append clock and EOPs to .vex file

  vex2obs --preobs cband1.vex

3. Edit .v2d file as appropriate

  - change machines, nCore, nThread 

4. Generate correlator jobs

  vex2difx cband1.v2d
 
5. Generate delay model

  difxcalc cband1*.calc

6. Update the filelist files for appropriate destinations

  - default is to place them in the local directory

7. Generate simulated data

  vdifsim -v cband1_*.input

8. Correlate the data

  startdifx -v -f -n cband1_*.input

9. Generate a FITS file

  difx2fits cband1_*.difx CBAND1.FITS
